// This is the COMPLETE Unicode emoji pattern - ~3600 emoji including:
// - All base emoji (smileys, people, nature, food, activities, objects, symbols, flags)
// - ZWJ sequences (👨‍❤️‍👨, 👩‍💻, etc.)
// - Skin tone modifiers
// - Regional indicator pairs (flags)
// - Variation selectors
//
// Used for both:
// 1. Detecting whether text starts with an emoji (for habit tracking, etc.)
// 2. Building the autocomplete dictionary for `:` triggers in the editor
//
// The compactPattern is created by replacing \\uXXXX escapes with actual Unicode
// characters, which dramatically reduces file size and parse time.

/** Full emoji regex (with \uXXXX escapes). */
